## Bead Tracking

- Every unit of work is a **bead** (stored in `.forge/beads/active/`)
- Beads track: status, risk tier, files modified, pipeline stage, checkpoints
- The pre-edit hook blocks file changes without an active bead
- Use `/deliver --quick` for lightweight changes with minimal ceremony
